attachments.title: Joseph Rose: Left? Right? Portland's 'left-sided' bike lane on North Williams creates passing chaos (video)
attachments.text: The Portland Bureau of Transportation has decided to shake things up on North Williams Avenue, along what is essentially a one-way bicycle superhighway cutting through North Portland.
